data.description: Welcome to your dream home! Situated on a spacious lot, this beautifully designed 4 bed, 2.5 bath residence located in Keswick Estates subdivision is everything you're looking for. Upon entry, an inviting 2 story foyer w/crown molding & wainscoting leads to a flex room off to your right. The open concept living area boasts a spacious living room with a cozy fireplace perfect for family gatherings. A well-appointed kitchen featuring ample cabinetry, a large island, granite counter tops, subway tile back splash, and stainless-steel appliances, everything you need for hosting or just your everyday living needs. The Owner’s Suite is a retreat with an abundant amount of space, a sitting area, massive walk-in closet with hardwood flooring, and high vaulted ceilings.  Upstairs are also 3 additional spacious bedrooms with ample closet space and a full bath. The backyard consists of a covered patio and fenced yard ensuring privacy, while the generous spacing between homes adds to the sense of tranquility. Conveniently located near shopping, schools, and restaurants. Just mins from Fayetteville Pavilion. About 20 mins from Hartsfield-Jackson Airport. Refrigerator, washer/dryer, and shed all included. Don’t miss out on this opportunity to call this home yours.
